    <string name="pay_error">System error, please try again later</string>
    <string name="pay_huawei_rule">1. Coins purchased can only be used in this application.\n2. Payment: The purchase will be charged to your HUAWEI account.\n3. Renewal: Your HUAWEI account will be charged within 24 hours before the expiration and the subscription period will be extended for another subscription cycle upon successful deduction.\n4. Cancellation: To cancel the subscription renewal, please disable the automatic renewal feature in the HUAWEI Subscriptions - Manage Settings section at least 24 hours before the current subscription period expires. \n5. Payment successful but recharge not taking effect for an extended period? &lt;a href=refresh_pay&gt;Click here to refresh&lt;/a&gt; or send an email to: moboreels@moboreader.com.\n6. Manage your subscriptions: You can &lt;a href=to_subscriptions_path&gt;view, change, or cancel your subscriptions.&lt;/a&gt;</string>
    <string name="pay_unlock_tip">It takes %s Coins to unlock this episode</string>
    <string name="pay_xiaomi_rule">1. The coins you purchase can only be used within this app. 2. Payment: Once you confirm your purchase and make the payment, it is charged to your Xiaomi account. 3. Renewal: Your Xiaomi account is charged within 24 hours before the subscription expires, and the subscription renews for another cycle upon successful payment. 4. Canceling Renewal: To cancel renewal, manually turn off the auto-renewal feature in Xiaomi Subscriptions—Settings Management at least 24 hours before the current subscription period ends. 5. If your payment is successful but the recharge has not been processed for an extended period, please click here to refresh or email moboreels@moboreader.com. 6. Manage Subscriptions: You can check, change, or cancel your subscription anytime.</string>
